{
  "texts": [
    "Thus, the GNN is used both for encoding and decoding.",
    "The algorithm does not include operation flexibility.",
    "Hameed et al. (2023) also utilize a GNN for encoding state, enabling event-driven online scheduling decisions, but the algorithm lacks operational flexibility.",
    "Jing et al.",
    "propose a MARL based on a graph convolutional algorithm for FJSP, including routing and operational flexibility."
  ]
}